<div class="card">
  <div class="card-divider">
    <h2 class="card-title"><%= title %></h2>
  </div>

  <div class="card-section">
    <% if !@form.valid? %>
      <% form.object.errors.values.each do |message| %>
        <small class=""><%= message[0] %></small>
      <% end %>
    <% else %>
      <p>The definition for the election <strong><%= translated_attribute(election.title) %></strong> consists in <strong><%= election.questions.size %> questions </strong>and all of them are valid.</p>
      <p>The trustees that are going to participate in this election are:</p>
      <div class="table-scroll">
        <table class="table-list">
          <thead>
            <tr>
              <th><%= t("models.election.fields.user", scope: "decidim.elections") %></th>
              <th><%= t("models.election.fields.public_key", scope: "decidim.elections") %></th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            <% @form.trustees.each do |trustee| %>
              <tr data-id="<%= trustee.id %>">
                <td>
                  <%= trustee.user.name %>
                </td>
                <td>
                  <%= trustee.public_key %>
                </td>
              </tr>
              <%= form.hidden_field :trustee_ids, multiple: true, value: trustee.id %>
            <% end %>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
      <p>The size of this list of trustees is correct and it will be needed at least <strong>2 trustees</strong> to perform the tally process.</p>
    <% end %>
  </div>
</div>
